## BUILD PRICING LAMBDA ZIP

Before deploying, build the pricing Lambda zip:

```powershell
# Build pricing Lambda zip (stripe only — no requests needed)
$BuildDir = "backend-integration\lambda\pricing-build"
New-Item -ItemType Directory -Force -Path $BuildDir | Out-Null
Copy-Item backend-integration\lambda\pricing_lambda.py $BuildDir\
pip install stripe -t $BuildDir --quiet --break-system-packages
Compress-Archive -Path "$BuildDir\*" `
  -DestinationPath "backend-integration\lambda\pricing_lambda.zip" -Force
Remove-Item -Recurse -Force $BuildDir
Write-Host "Pricing Lambda zip built"
```

